then, was based on this survey,

00:36:42.580 --> 00:36:46.110
it is basically an
open and traverse,

00:36:46.110 --> 00:36:48.830
which simply involved measuring
the straight line distance

00:36:48.830 --> 00:36:51.670
between each major
turn during the journey

00:36:51.670 --> 00:36:54.330
and recording each compass
bearing of the next turn.

00:36:54.330 --> 00:36:56.160
They had five separate
compasses with them.

00:36:56.160 --> 00:37:01.030
The compass relied on
this 300 years earlier.

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:02.620
So nothing changed much.

00:37:02.620 --> 00:37:04.000
