they had with grizzly bears.

00:47:33.900 --> 00:47:36.430
They chased some of their
soldiers open to trees.

00:47:36.430 --> 00:47:38.240
The chased them into the rivers.

00:47:38.240 --> 00:47:40.300
They would shoot these
bears five and six times,

00:47:40.300 --> 00:47:42.320
and it didn't kill
them, and so, yeah,

00:47:42.320 --> 00:47:46.100
the grizzly bear was probably the
most significant natural history

00:47:46.100 --> 00:47:48.380
specimen they encountered.

00:47:48.380 --> 00:47:49.680
Yes?

00:47:49.680 --> 00:47:53.810
&gt;&gt; Audience Speaker: I'd
